<h3>Process</h3>
<p>
  We initially decided the application would be most useful to mobile users. 
  As we were most familiar with the iPhone platform, we began with an iPhone
  application, however we quickly decided that we needed to be able to reach a
  greater audience.
  
  So we created a mobile web application. Although it was developed primarily for
  the iPhone, it works on the Android platform, and FIXME...
  
  An added benefit of this approach is that it was simple to create a website
  accessible from any computer. Although not as useful to such users as it is to
  mobile users on the go, we envisage users using the website to plan trips before time.
</p>

